\par Subject: Berlin Morale Report No.34 
\par 
\par Attached is a report on Berlin Morale No.34 for the first half of December.
\par 
\par Readers are asked to remember that although this report is compiled as objectively as possible, opinions expressed may often seem
 critical and captious. This is because so-called "opinion formers" among the German population may often be ill informed. PORO is not responsible for the views of the German population but is concerned only with the accuracy of the reporting.
